	(text "The boot loader is located in system memory. It is used to reprogram the flash memory by\nusing USART1 (PA9/PA10), USART3 (PC10/PC11 or PB10/PB11), CAN2 (PB5/PB13), USB\nOTG FS in Device mode (PA11/PA12) through DFU (device firmware upgrade)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
